      "id": "746e58a0f9005bae",
      "text": "Bringing sustainability into the vision of the future\nWith a sketch of the desired future that you and your main stakeholders can agree on at hand, when can we validly call the end state we see as ideal for us as sustainable or contributing to sustainable development?\nHere, the challenge is not so much answering the above-mentioned strategic questions in an ambitious or even utopian way. We all know how to do that."
