      "text": "Sustainability is a matter of enabling or impairing our future generations of people to have a better life. Therefore, sustainability proposals that imply liabilities of future generations would render a sustainability strategy trivial and perhaps even misleading. Such an approach cannot be called a sustainability strategy."
